---
import LightLayout from '../layouts/LightLayout.astro';
---

<LightLayout title="Data Deletion Request — My Site" description="Request deletion of your data associated with My Site's advertising management tools. We process all requests within 30 days.">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-headline text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tightest mb-8">
        Data Deletion Request
      </h1>
      <p class="text-warm-gray text-sm mb-8">Last updated: April 5, 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-warm-gray text-base leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-xl text-espresso mb-3">How to Request Deletion</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">To request deletion of your data associated with My Site's advertising management tools, please email <a href="mailto:privacy@example.com" class="text-deep-teal transition-opacity duration-150 ease-out-expo hover:opacity-80 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-deep-teal active:opacity-60">privacy@example.com</a> with the subject line "Data Deletion Request."</p>
          <p class="mb-3">Please include the following in your request:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Your name</li>
            <li>The email address associated with your account</li>
            <li>Your Facebook or Meta user ID (if known)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-xl text-espresso mb-3">What Data We Collect</h2>
          <p>In connection with our advertising management services, we may collect and process ad account data from platforms such as Meta (Facebook) for the purpose of managing and optimizing advertising campaigns on your behalf.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-xl text-espresso mb-3">Processing Timeframe</h2>
          <p>We will process your deletion request within 30 days of receipt. If additional time is required, we will notify you of the reason and expected completion date.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-xl text-espresso mb-3">Confirmation</h2>
          <p>Once your data has been deleted, you will receive a confirmation email at the address you provided in your request.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-xl text-espresso mb-3">Questions</h2>
          <p>For questions about our data practices, please see our <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-deep-teal transition-opacity duration-150 ease-out-expo hover:opacity-80 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-deep-teal active:opacity-60">Privacy Policy</a> or contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@example.com" class="text-deep-teal transition-opacity duration-150 ease-out-expo hover:opacity-80 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-deep-teal active:opacity-60">privacy@example.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</LightLayout>
